---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection';
import Reviews from '../../components/Reviews';
import ServiceForm from '../../components/ServiceForm';
import LicenseBadges from '../../components/LicenseBadges.astro';
import BrandsSection from '../../components/BrandsSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="HVAC Services in Garden Grove, CA | HiLo Heating & Air" description="Fast, professional AC repair, heating service, and HVAC maintenance in Garden Grove, CA. Same-day service from licensed technicians at HiLo Heating & Air.">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-blue-800 py-20 sm:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Air Conditioning Repair Garden Grove</h1>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Summers in Southern California don't mess around, and when your AC quits on a 95-degree afternoon, you need someone who actually picks up the phone.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-10 pb-4 sm:py-16 sm:pb-6 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <LicenseBadges />
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-10 items-start">
          <div>
            <span class="inline-block bg-brand-blue/10 text-brand-blue text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4">Schedule Service</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-4">Get a Free Estimate</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Fill out the form and our team will get back to you within 15 minutes. Same-day service available.</p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Same-Day Service Available</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Free Diagnostics with Repair</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0115.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 013 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 003 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Upfront Pricing, No Hidden Fees</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ServiceForm client:load />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mt-0 mb-4">AC Repair Services in Garden Grove</h2>

        <p>Summers in Southern California don't mess around, and when your AC quits on a 95-degree afternoon, you need someone who actually picks up the phone. That's been HiLo Heating and Air's whole approach to <strong>air conditioning repair Garden Grove</strong> homeowners for years now — show up fast, fix it right, charge a fair price.</p>

        <h2>Why Locals Keep Calling Us</h2>
        <p>Garden Grove's dry heat is brutal on cooling systems, whether it's an older unit tucked into a Magnolia Park bungalow or a newer high-efficiency setup near Brookhurst. Parts wear out. Refrigerant leaks. Capacitors die without warning. When that happens, our <strong>air conditioning repair Garden Grove</strong> crew gets out to your place quickly, often the same day, and figures out what's actually wrong instead of throwing parts at the problem and hoping.</p>
        <p>We get it — a dead AC isn't just annoying, it can be genuinely dangerous for kids, older folks, or anyone with health issues. So we don't drag our feet. Most calls get a technician on-site within hours, and most repairs — leaks, compressor trouble, bad capacitors, thermostat glitches — get handled in one trip because our trucks are stocked for it.</p>

        <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
        <p>A lot of the bigger outfits send whoever's free that day, and you never know who's showing up or what they'll try to sell you. HiLo Heating and Air built its name in Orange County doing the opposite: same trusted techs, honest diagnoses, no pressure to replace a system that just needs a fix. People ask for <strong>air conditioning repair Garden Grove</strong> specifically because their neighbors told them we don't pad the bill or push unnecessary upgrades.</p>
        <p>Our team trains regularly on whatever's in your garage — Carrier, Trane, Lennox, Goodman, Rheem, doesn't matter. That training, plus trucks stocked with common parts, is why so many <strong>air conditioning repair Garden Grove</strong> jobs wrap up in a single visit rather than dragging into a second appointment.</p>

        <h2>Full Repair Lineup</h2>
        <p>Here's what we handle:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Refrigerant leak detection and recharge</li>
          <li>Compressor and condenser repair</li>
          <li>Capacitor and electrical troubleshooting</li>
          <li>Thermostat setup and calibration</li>
          <li>Airflow and ductwork checks</li>
          <li>After-hours emergency repair</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Every job comes with an upfront quote before we touch anything, plus a satisfaction guarantee. No surprise charges tacked on at the end.</p>

        <h2>Ready to Get Your AC Fixed?</h2>
        <p>A small AC issue today can turn into an expensive replacement if it sits too long. Call HiLo Heating and Air, and find out firsthand why Garden Grove families keep coming back to us for <strong>air conditioning repair Garden Grove</strong> services they can actually trust.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    

    <Reviews client:visible />
    <BrandsSection />

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-slate-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">How quickly can someone get to my house?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Usually same-day. If it's urgent, we'll often have a tech there within a few hours.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">How do I know if my AC actually needs repair?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Warm air blowing instead of cold, strange rattling or grinding noises, the unit cycling on and off too much, or your energy bill creeping up for no reason — all worth a look.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Can you come out on weekends or evenings?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes. We run emergency repair appointments outside normal business hours too.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">What's this going to cost me?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Depends on the problem, but you'll get a clear price before we start — never a surprise bill later.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Do you work on every brand?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Pretty much — Carrier, Trane, Lennox, Goodman, Rheem, and most others you'll find around Garden Grove.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Should I just replace my unit instead of repairing it?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Sometimes, but we won't push you that direction unless it genuinely makes sense given the unit's age and condition.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Got any maintenance plans?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yep, seasonal plans that catch small problems before they turn into expensive ones.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Are your techs actually licensed?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Every one of them — licensed, insured, background-checked.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-brand-blue/5 py-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-brand-blue font-semibold">HiLo Heating and Air · 8131 Electric Ave, Stanton, CA 90680, United States</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-1"><a href="tel:+17148535534" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">(714) 853-5534</a> · <a href="mailto:info@hiloheatingandair.com" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">info@hiloheatingandair.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <CTASection client:visible />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
